{
  "text": "MNLI [CITATION_1] ) is a collection of 433k sentence pairs manually annotated with contradiction, entailment, or neutral relations. Finetuning with this dataset leads to accuracy improvement on all GLUE tasks except CoLA [CITATION_2] .",
